{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"923ebe5cdd","title":"和军委电台部分同志的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3e10136efc","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":25,"articleId":"923ebe5cdd"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d6cf6a9965","type":"paragraph","text":"和军委电台部分同志的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"923ebe5cdd"},{"id":"b44832ab8e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月25日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"923ebe5cdd"},{"id":"728bae1f6c","type":"paragraph","text":"革命嘛，总是难免走点弯路，总是要吃点苦的。如果有人因为吃了点苦，就不愿意在四方面军工作，那就不对了，四方面军也是党领导的军队嘛！我们干革命，就得听党的话，就要服从革命的需要，哪里需要我们，就到哪里去，革命事业嘛，总得有个分工，分到哪里，就在哪里战斗，不能挑挑拆栋。如果，认为革命工作有高低贵残之分的话，那是不对的","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"923ebe5cdd"},{"id":"0a2082887c","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]在长征的路上被分配去左路军工作的军委电台的部分同志来到保安。由于张国寿的错误路线，他们走了许多宽柱路，吃了不少苦，觉得心里委屈，工作上不安心。毛泽东得知后便去驻地看望他们，同他们进行了亲切的交谈。这是毛泽东等和他们谈话的部分内容。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"923ebe5cdd"}],"page":{"id":"52bdcb29df","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"923ebe5cdd","start":220,"end":220}}}},"__N_SSG":true}